    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce2a",
      "text": "[/villagepump/二人称代名詞「あなた」に関する調査報告#627fb2a7aff09e00002f1eec]を見て理解が進んだ[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461887
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce2b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce2c",
      "text": "Q: どういう時に議論で人を指し示すことが必要か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce2d",
      "text": "A: 視点によって見え方が異なることを指摘する時[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce2e",
      "text": "　多くの場合「[視点]」には名前がついておらず「誰の視点」という形でしか表現できない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce2f",
      "text": "　そこで例えば「あなたの視点ではX≒Yだが、私の視点ではX≠Yである、これは両立しうる」などのような表現が必要になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce30",
      "text": " 　[https://gyazo.com/6c2d7be5e47635516bdf4021f4ec504b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce31",
      "text": " \t　(from [意味の交差点とは何か？])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461895
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce32",
      "text": "　過去の実例を振り返ってみると、僕が議論で「あなた」を使い始めた時、「[観測範囲]」や「[理解]」「[解釈]」「[主観]」などの「個々人に紐づいているもの」に関する言及を伴っていることが多い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce33",
      "text": "　[視点]について整理した: [Aから見てBがXだが、Bから見てAもX]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce35",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce36",
      "text": "\t[/villagepump/意見対意見の議論なら人称を省ける？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653462165
    },
    {
      "id": "628dd366aff09e000087ce37",
      "text": "　[メタ認知]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653461863,
      "updated": 1653461863
    },
